The paper deals with the coverage analysis of a cellular massive MIMO network which adopts 3D beamforming. This involves the use of stochastic geometry framework and optimization techniques to find the optimum tilt angle of the base station antenna pattern. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.IT (Information Theory), cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), cs.SY (Systems and Control), cs.MM (Multimedia), and cs.MA (Multiagent Systems).
